jdk17一样有这个问题！

环境：
jshell 17.0.1
openjdk version &#34;17.0.1&#34; 2021-10-19 LTS
OpenJDK Runtime Environment Zulu17.30+15-CA (build 17.0.1+12-LTS)
OpenJDK 64-Bit Server VM Zulu17.30+15-CA (build 17.0.1+12-LTS, mixed mode, sharing)

iterm2 Build 3.4.12
zsh 5.8 (arm-apple-darwin21.1.0)

OS:
Darwin localhost 21.1.0 Darwin Kernel Version 21.1.0: Wed Oct 13 17:33:01 PDT 2021; root:xnu-8019.41.5~1/RELEASE_ARM64_T6000 arm64

----------------------------------
表现：
jshell&gt; greeting = switch (language) {
   ...&gt; case &#34;English&#34; -&gt; &#34;Hello&#34;;
   ...&gt; case &#34;Spanish&#34; -&gt; &#34;Hola&#34;;
   ...&gt; case &#34;Chinese&#34; -&gt; &#34;你好&#34;;
   ...&gt; default -&gt; throw new RuntimeException(&#34;Unsupported language&#34;);
| Error:
| reached end of file while parsing
| default -&gt; throw new RuntimeException(&#34;Unsupported language&#34;);
|                                                                                              ^

只要试图在^的位置换行，就会报错；如果不换行，直接在后面写“}” 就正常了：

jshell&gt; greeting = switch (language) {
   ...&gt; case &#34;English&#34; -&gt; &#34;Hello&#34;;
   ...&gt; case &#34;Spanish&#34; -&gt; &#34;Hola&#34;;
   ...&gt; case &#34;Chinese&#34; -&gt; &#34;你好&#34;;
   ...&gt; default -&gt; throw new RuntimeException(&#34;Unsupported language&#34;);}
greeting ==&gt; &#34;Hello&#34;
| assigned to greeting : String
